## Privacy Policy

Beat my Time! does not collect, store, or share any personal information or data from users. The app does not track users or interact with any third-party services that collect personal data.
For any inquiries, feel free to contact us at: beatmytime2s@gmail.com

## Game Center

Our app integrates with Apple's Game Center to provide features like leaderboards and achievements. Game Center requires the player to log in with their Apple ID to use these features. We do not collect or store any personal data related to Game Center. 
For more information on how Apple handles Game Center data, please refer to Apple's Privacy Policy at [https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/](https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/).

Effective Date: 08/09/2024
